text: Dündar Ali Osman (, ; 30 December 1930 – 18 January 2021), also known as Dündar Ali Osman Osmanoğlu was the 45th Head of the House of Osman from 2017 until his death. He was born in Damascus, Syria. Osman died on 18 January 2021 in Istanbul, Turkey at the age of 90.Sabah, Daily. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2021 deaths Category:House of Osman
